tourBios.curYrHigh: Joined PGA TOUR Latinoamérica with a ninth-place finish at the Argentina Q-School in January.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Played college golf for the University of South Florida from 2011-15...Won two college events, the Wexford Plantation Invitational and the Florida State Collegiate...Three-time All-Conference... Named Big East Freshman of the Year in 2011-12...Named team MVP over four consecutive years at Viera High School.
tourBios.personal: Has one sister, Tia, who is popular on Instagram under the name @tortillaa...Earliest and favorite golf memory is a hole-in-one he made at age 10...Biggest thrill in golf was winning his first college event, in 2013...Odell Beckham, Jr. is his favorite athlete outside golf, and the San Francisco 49ers are his favorite pro team...Twitter and Instagram name is @treyV1
tourBios.exmtStatus: Finished 2-11 at 2016 Q-School (exempt to midseason reshuffle)
